    dc:description "FIGURE 21. Termitozophilus tenebrus sp. nov. A) Head, dorsal view. B) Left and right mandibles, dorsal view. C) Labrum, dorsal view. D) Maxilla, dorsal view. E) Pre-mentum, mentum and sub-mentum, ventral view. Scales: A = 2 mm; D = 1,5 mm; E = 1 mm; B, C = 0,5 mm." ;
