    dc:description "FIGURE 6. Termitozophilus favachoi sp. nov. A) Meso-metaventrite, ventral view. B) Meso-metanotum and tergite I, dorsal view. C) Elytron, dorsal view. D) Tergite VII, dorsal view. E) Median lobe of aedeagus, lateral view. F) Male sternite IX, ventral view. G) Tergite VIII, dorsal view. H) Sternite VIII, ventral view. I) Female tergites IX and X, dorsal view. J) Aedeagus, paramere, lateral view. K) Spermatheca, lateral view. Scales: A, B, H, I = 2 mm; C, D, F, G = 1,5 mm; K = 0,5 mm; E= 0,2 mm; J = 0,1 mm." ;
